author: Nerdstalgic
description:
With 11 movies (and counting), the Fast & Furious franchise has become one of the most successful and explosive film series of all time. What started in 2001 as a street-racing cult classic has transformed into a global action juggernaut packed with high-octane car chases, death-defying stunts, and a cast of characters bonded by one word — family.

Today, we're diving deep into the iconic moments, jaw-dropping set pieces, and behind-the-scenes stories that made this franchise a box office phenomenon.
